# HealthCare Plus Medical Centre Website

A modern, responsive medical practice website built for Dr. Sarah Mitchell at HealthCare Plus Medical Centre. This project showcases a professional healthcare website with clean design, smooth animations, and full mobile responsiveness.

![HealthCare Plus Preview](https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1631815588090-d4bfec5b1ccb?w=800)

