## âœ¨ Features

- **Fully Responsive Design** - Works flawlessly on all devices (320px to 1920px+)
- **Modern UI/UX** - Clean, professional healthcare aesthetic
- **Smooth Animations** - Subtle transitions and scroll-based animations
- **Accessibility Ready** - WCAG compliant with reduced motion support
- **Fast Performance** - Optimized for Core Web Vitals
- **SEO Friendly** - Semantic HTML and meta tags

