## ğŸ¨ Design System

### Colors
```css
--brand-deep: #005C65;    /* Deep teal */
--brand-primary: #008487; /* Primary teal */
--accent: #D87C7C;        /* Coral accent */
--neutral-50: #F7F7F5;    /* Light background */
--neutral-900: #444444;   /* Dark text */
```

### Typography
- **Font Family:** Poppins (400, 500, 600, 700)
- **Base Size:** 16px
- **Line Height:** 1.6 - 1.8

## ğŸš€ Deployment

This site is configured for deployment on [Vercel](https://vercel.com).

### Deploy to Vercel

1. Fork or clone this repository
2. Import project to Vercel
3. Deploy automatically

[![Deploy with Vercel](https://vercel.com/button)](https://vercel.com/new/clone?repository-url=https://github.com/yourusername/healthcare-plus)

### Manual Deployment

```bash
# Install Vercel CLI
npm install -g vercel

# Login to Vercel
vercel login

# Deploy
vercel
```

